♪ Life's no dress rehearsal ♪

53:52.833 --> 53:58.458
♪ So why not make some waves
Before it's through? ♪

53:58.541 --> 54:01.041
♪ Go big or you've blown it ♪

54:01.625 --> 54:03.583
♪ It's time that I own it! ♪

54:03.666 --> 54:04.833
Yes, ma'am!

54:04.916 --> 54:09.166
♪ Let's make it clear
That tonight belongs to you ♪

54:09.250 --> 54:10.250
What?

54:10.333 --> 54:14.125
♪ Belongs to me! ♪

54:14.208 --> 54:16.791
Oh, God,
I can't believe this is finally happening.

54:16.875 --> 54:19.458
I know.
She almost ruined it for all of us.

54:19.541 --> 54:21.666
Well, what goes around comes around.

54:21.750 --> 54:24.541
-You look hot.
-You look so hot.

54:25.833 --> 54:28.916
♪ Well, I hate to sound conceited ♪

54:29.000 --> 54:32.666
♪ But the boys get overheated ♪

54:32.750 --> 54:36.416
♪ When I strike a pose or two like thus ♪

54:38.375 --> 54:41.541
♪ And you have to hand it to me ♪

54:41.625 --> 54:44.875
♪ I mean, even I would do me ♪

54:44.958 --> 54:47.791
♪ Let's show the world tonight belongs ♪

54:47.875 --> 54:51.458
♪ To us ♪

