♪ Life's no dress rehearsal ♪

54:57.583 --> 55:01.333
♪ Excuse me while I state the obvious ♪

55:03.583 --> 55:06.083
♪ Go big or you've blown it ♪

55:06.708 --> 55:09.416
♪ It's time that we own it ♪

55:10.041 --> 55:13.708
♪ And make it clear
That tonight belongs to us ♪

55:16.666 --> 55:19.583
Alyssa, you look so beautiful.

55:19.666 --> 55:22.291
You should always
wear your hair like this.

55:22.375 --> 55:23.708
-Mom.
-Yeah?

55:23.791 --> 55:26.125
I just want you to know
what's gonna happen tonight.

55:26.208 --> 55:28.541
No. Can we not spoil this, please?

55:28.625 --> 55:32.416
I have worked so hard for tonight.
I have a right to enjoy it too.

55:33.000 --> 55:36.416
You are going to have
a wonderful prom like a normal girl.

55:36.500 --> 55:40.208
-I've made sure of that.
-What is that supposed to mean?

55:41.625 --> 55:44.333
♪ I don't like
When strangers get in my way ♪

55:44.416 --> 55:47.416
♪ Or anyone who messes with the PTA ♪

55:47.500 --> 55:49.833
♪ Well, maybe that's just me ♪

55:49.916 --> 55:53.958
♪ But trust me
Fixing little problems is what I do ♪

55:54.041 --> 55:56.916
♪ Now everyone is happy
I promise you ♪

55:57.000 --> 56:02.166
♪ And I would never
Miss a night like this ♪

56:02.250 --> 56:03.500
♪ Alyssa ♪

56:03.583 --> 56:06.375
♪ You're my superstar ♪

56:06.458 --> 56:11.541
♪ Now get your ass in the car ♪

56:12.416 --> 56:14.125
[upbeat dance music playing]

56:14.208 --> 56:15.958
[crowd cheering]

